@startuml
actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer
boundary "Vessel Visit Notification Management API" as System

== Approve Vessel Visit Notification ==
Officer -> System : PUT /api/vesselvisitnotification/accept/id/{id}
System --> Officer : 200 OK\nBody: VesselVisitNotificationDto\n(status="Accepted", assignedDockId, processedBy, processedAt, tasks)

== Reject Vessel Visit Notification ==
Officer -> System : PUT /api/vesselvisitnotification/reject/\nBody: RejectVesselVisitNotificationDto
System --> Officer : 200 OK\nBody: VesselVisitNotificationDto\n(status="Rejected", rejectionReason, processedBy, processedAt)

@enduml
